Participating Mission Members:

The pod that Jiiro mentions, it's an averagely large massive metallic pod that has holographic screens displayed over them with categories of weapons to digi-print, along with a ballistic vest choice that will likely reduce the lethality of a projectile, should you get hit by one or some while out in 'N'. Equipment of these weapons and armor will be temporary and only permitted for use in the mission segment, as equipment will be deconstructed if they are still intact upon return in order to conserve city resources.

Dotted around the massive field that stands behind the sealed blast shield known as 'Gate 7', there are dozens of transport vehicles that are similar to warthogs in the Halo series, just without the turret and more seats. There are also small birds that are quick and versatile, only carrying up to two on the side-seats via attached platform seats and a seat belt strap with the third being the pilot of a trained professional pilot. There is no team assigned for anyone yet, as you are provided gear and told to standby near the pod when complete.

- Handheld C4 Launcher

- Shovel Launcher
